- install heroku gem

- create SSH keys (http://devcenter.heroku.com/articles/keys)

* send the public key to heroku
  'heroku keys:add'

* create heroku app:
  'heroku create awayday'

- enter account info (it will submit your public key to heroku)

* add MongoLab to the heroku app
  'heroku addons:add mongolab:starter'

* push the app to heroku
  'git push heroku master'
